[Mouse Action]
Left Button      : rotate around X/Y axis (or stretching box)
Right Button     : move object (or box)
Middle Button    : toggle lighting (or change lighting position)
Ctrl+Left Button : rotate around Z axis
Ctrl+Right Button: zoom in/out object (or box) 

[Keyboard Mapping]
Home             : reset the scene
Space            : go to next task
F10              : enable/disable boxes
F5               : toggle synchronization(in multiview mode)
F4               : remove the most recently visited box
F3               : add a box by duplicating the most recently visited
F2               : toggle associate interplay among boxes (AND/OR)
F1               : toggle interaction prompt text
d                : toggle color/monochromatic rendering
m                : alternating color encoding
n                : next DWI image
o                : toggle DWI image embedding
p                : previous DWI image
r                : switch between selection/removal mode of box
